# A Beginner's Guide to Forms in React

Forms are an essential part of web applicationsâ€”they allow users to interact with your app by submitting data. In React, handling forms may feel different compared to traditional HTML due to React's stateful, component-based architecture. This guide walks you through the fundamentals of working with forms in React, ensuring you feel confident building interactive and user-friendly forms.

